                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-51-off268 t18300916-51-crimeloc271"></join> about eleven o'clock at night, on the 21st of August, going the nearest way home from Covent-garden; the prisoner came and took my hat off - he was standing near Great Russell-street; he seemed to be alone - he ran off with it; I pursued, and got my hat from the Policeman, who took it from the prisoner.</p>
